OL,3,CMan, 30, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Belfast stabbing attack
OL,6,FA man arrested on suspicion of the
OL,7,FBelfast knife attack has been charged
OL,8,Fwith attempted murder, police have
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe 30-year-old accused, who is
OL,12,FSudanese, is also charged with
OL,13,Fpossession of an article with a blade
OL,14,For point in a public place and making
OL,15,Fthreats to kill.
OL,17,FHe is due to appear at Belfast
OL,18,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
