OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1781121970
OL,3,CMan, 30, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Belfast stabbing attack
OL,6,FThe victim of the attack, a man aged
OL,7,Fin his 40s, remained in a serious
OL,8,Fcondition in hospital on Tuesday,
OL,9,Freceiving treatment for serious eye,
OL,10,Fface and back injuries.
OL,12,FThere has been widespread condemnation
OL,13,Fof Monday night's knife assault. The
OL,14,Fprime minister said the attack was
OL,15,F"sickening".
OL,17,F"I have absolutely no tolerance for
OL,18,Fabhorrent scenes of violence like this
OL,19,Fon our streets," he said.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@AOU
