OL,3,CMan, 30, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Belfast stabbing attack
OL,6,FEarlier, the leaders of the five
OL,7,Flargest parties at Stormont issued a
OL,8,Fjoint statement in response to the
OL,9,Fattack.
OL,11,FSinn Fein vice president Ms O'Neill,
OL,12,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson, Alliance
OL,13,FParty leader Ms Long, UUP leader Jon
OL,14,FBurrows and SDLP leader Claire Hanna
OL,15,Fsaid they were "united in our
OL,16,Fcondemnation of the horrific incident
OL,17,Fin North Belfast last night".
OL,26,@sD@GrrwD@POUyD@\O]
