OL,3,CMan, 30, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Belfast stabbing attack
OL,6,FPolice commanders and political
OL,7,Fleaders have appealed for calm amid
OL,8,Fconcern anti-immigration protests
OL,9,Fplanned in Northern Ireland on Tuesday
OL,10,Fevening could turn violent.
