PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1781121970
OL,3,CMan, 30, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Belfast stabbing attack
OL,6,FCrowds were beginning to gather at
OL,7,Fsites in Belfast following a knife
OL,8,Fattack in the north of the city, with
OL,9,Fdozens of police officers deployed to
OL,10,Fblock protesters moving along
OL,11,FPortswood Road as they walked from the
OL,12,FHighfield House Hotel.
OL,14,FDetectives have said there is no
OL,15,Findication the attack was terror-
OL,16,Frelated.
OL,18,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,19,Fhas launched a "critical incident" in
OL,20,Fresponse to the incident which was
OL,21,Fcaptured on video.
OL,26,@{D@POU{D@bO]
