OL,3,CMan, 30, charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cafter Belfast stabbing attack
OL,6,FThe clip shows people, including one
OL,7,Fwith a hurling stick, intervening to
OL,8,Fstop the man attacking the victim in
OL,9,Fthe Kinnaird Avenue residential area
OL,10,Fclose to the busy Antrim Road in north
OL,11,FBelfast.
